buy 20 sharpening stones and 20 water flasks. 

then loot or buy rusty mace/warhammer/scimitar/long sword/broad sword/morning star/battle axe
put the rusty weapon and a sharpening stone in a forge and it becomes a "tarnished" weapon (smithing 21-25) 

now take the tarnished weapon in the forge again with a water flask and it becomes: a SMALL BRICK OF ORE (smithing 21). 

even if you start with a smithing skill of 1 you should be able to get 1-3 bricks out of 20 weapons - and you skill will rise too.

of course you can buy it from vendors who label "smithing supplies" sometimes, but thats not as satisfying ;)

